snippet.title: Russiagate Hoax against Trump: “OBAMA DID IT!”
snippet.description:
Judicial Watch President @TomFitton appeared on "The Larry O'Connor Show" to discuss the Obama FBI's targeting of Donald Trump using the anti-Trump dossier from former British intelligence operative Christopher Steele.
